Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部呼叫401
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續還擊敵人 並向9點方向移動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後轉由西寧格卿指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再追了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在保護總督是最優先的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 但現在無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來發佈撤退命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再磨磨蹭蹭的話會全軍覆沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確…確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見呢 居然動搖到連指令都無法發佈的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是柯內莉婭的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 槍不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我昏迷的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誰拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的樣子被人看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少有兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍的人和被打中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共有兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼早 你在做什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫信嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是情書之類的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對象是魯魯修?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見尤菲米婭殿下?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我想向她道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒店劫持事件時她保護了妮娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說『我是尤菲米婭』 挺身而出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想見見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是公主殿下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能入贅的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為有這種不純動機的人是見不到她的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不純…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉還真是嚴苛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算魯魯修不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也不要向我發洩邪惡的情感衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我也想見見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米婭殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒… 但是 對方是高不可攀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這裡是阿斯福德學園學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那裡有什麼異常的情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉好像也沒有出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近上課也常常請假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也稍微認真點當個學生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 好你個『優等生』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否替我轉告娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說今天會遲點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是『今天會』而是『今天也會』吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是不能見面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要在同一所學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿瑟 啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩什麼啊 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 朱雀看來不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 『被軍隊發現』這種可能就排除了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了軍隊和黑之騎士團以外 我不認為還有其他人會去那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有日本解放戰線的倖存者這一可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只偷走了槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經讓扇注意黑市的情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血液樣本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然採集了 但化驗還需要時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我隱約覺得在那戰場上看到了莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 和你接吻的那個女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糾纏不休!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想確認一下罷了 你這『好色小鬼』!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是如此 那我們當前應該徹查的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是本次作戰 還是成田連山那次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明顯是針對公主殿下的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擒賊先擒王是戰爭的常理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有克洛維斯殿下的事亦是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說ZERO是針對布里塔尼亞的體制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如說可能是針對布里塔尼亞皇族的復仇行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了民眾挺身而出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心啊 尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想再經歷『酒店劫持』那樣的事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓殿下擁有一位『騎士』如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『騎士』?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警衛一職由尤菲米婭大人的專屬騎士來擔當的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能以那人為中心建立親衛隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米婭大人身為副總督
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已有此權利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初 本以為是由於他天性溫柔的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你不認為他對人命消逝的反應太敏感了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際行動數據中並沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便 我還想試試那個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那還在調整中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 無論你是否把朱雀當成零件看待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若不好好面對的話 就什麼也看不透 什麼也無法傳達的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 倒是你該不會把他看成是某人的替身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只會對奇怪的事情感覺敏銳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹也算是你上司嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等房間內的殺菌消毒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我非得去檢查別人的內衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人情可是很貴的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你自己來做不是更快嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩應該不會介意讓喜歡的男生來…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又拘泥於奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 槍沒找到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日記也只寫到14日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14日?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她父親死去的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺招人憐愛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為嫌疑犯來說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用那種說法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很壯觀的慰靈碑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉·菲尼特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會連那白色機甲一起消滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:08:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像玉城 一下子就被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放戰線的船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會爆炸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有過聯絡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過將去救援
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是為了這個ZERO才行動的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得那是看他相貌的機會?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是在懷疑ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說『時間實在太湊巧了』是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那真是ZERO搞的鬼 你打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那種口吻是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 迪特哈魯特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你好像因為害怕而逃跑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是膽小的布里塔尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用這種口氣對我們幹部問這問那的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是承擔了戰況調查的任務而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇也認可了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO也說無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫莎莉的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是討厭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼要去成田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是因為真面目可能被她知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是被知道了 怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉她嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正不想失去的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該遠遠避開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 經驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是生存的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是過分的男人呢 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連魯魯的事也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直在欺騙你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己就是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是用下達殺害你父親命令的那張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪去了你的吻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不可原諒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要受到懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是他 還有你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就是ZERO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真令人驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到那學生自己就是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是布里塔尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把這傢伙交給柯內莉婭總督
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能成為貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是騎士侯那種 而是真正的貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的處刑會比較適合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會對總督提及你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大意了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你的男人吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與ZERO同罪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你還以父親的死為代價 得到了回報
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我是… 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待他的溫柔 故意裝得可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同情的視線令你心情舒暢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想偽裝成悲劇的女主角到什麼時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想過那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪人性命勾引男人的你才不是什麼女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是醜惡的魔女才對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知魯魯修有其他喜歡的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還一直粘在他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該得到報應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓這種心情成為終生的傷痕?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自一人默默承受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪孽無法彌補 心靈也無法解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和魯魯修都太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為會是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能分頭去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 莎莉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在還問這種傻問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該不會在那的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是被知道了 怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉她嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙又在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙和莎莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次從頭開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說 在哪呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對莎莉做了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怕的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的女人被奪走不可原諒的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉在哪裡!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼來決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很擅長吧 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是繪畫的話 會用巴度安畫派(Batuan style)
;Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[巴度安畫派(Batuan style): 從三零年代開始 吸取了西方畫法的特點/N將畫中 人、神、惡魔 以極為細緻的畫法 展開為相當立體的動態畫作]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我等到你畫完嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託軍隊或警察會比較快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想招致不必要的麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就到高一點的地方眺望看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 魯魯修那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個目擊者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕下棋只是個幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的目的是把我帶到人跡罕至的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是第一次玩這個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打手機過來只是為了演戲?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是因為不知道我的長相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 沒有時間拿到我的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並不是準備周到的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機可趁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是把注意力集中在下棋上比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會輸的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼第一次玩 你這個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 正因為是你 所以才贏不了毛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這樣就算是… 我贏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然會一敗塗地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽C.C.說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我的真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在一瞬間就想到了14種可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且其中之一完全正確
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geass能力者!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的Geass如果沒有直接看到對方眼睛就無法生效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些規則我也全都知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解讀了我的思想!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Geass就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對莎莉開槍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 你把莎莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們開始玩懲罰遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的你不像平常的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有這種感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是… ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把槍是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是ZERO的… 魯魯的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Geass吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒對她用過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果你這麼做的話 我就會立刻開槍的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讀取的只有表層思想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也像我一樣有使用Geass的限制條件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:16:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延遲時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持續時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的目的到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是為了殺死我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你擅長的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓腦筋骨碌骨碌地轉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對偷吃的貓來說 這種死法最合適了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來贖罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會陪你一起死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也開槍了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對著另一個目擊者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護你的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個血跡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這一切結束吧 魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪孽應該受到懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 對莎莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能解讀思想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制人心 誘導其行為就異常簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別被騙了! 莎莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺騙了她的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果殺人是罪孽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要罪上加罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好口才 對什麼人就說什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的殺了人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會只是被這傢伙這樣誘導了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是自己察覺到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直隱瞞下去是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在猶豫什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是殺害了你的父親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙只是個殺人兇手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 這女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思維亂的一塌糊塗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 讓我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手! 住手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就由你們兩個人自己解決
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來還想弄得戲劇性一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣很無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就把他們兩人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然毫無察覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了嗎 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 毛 不是做得挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種打扮也很美啊 C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C. 我會來見你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會來見你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你居然會到人群中來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向人開槍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還向魯魯開槍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我竟然向魯魯開槍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的罪孽 全部由我來承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要你對我溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸明明死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願想起的事全部忘記就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來讓你全部忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親的事 我十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能有來生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也失去了家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 並不是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 或許是… 最重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些東西直到失去後才會意識到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意識到自己曾經從她的笑容中 得到過多少救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…無法再像以往那樣拌嘴 像以往那樣一起嬉笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經無法知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明一定會來臨的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然忘記了自己為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是為了替某件事畫上句號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實會有很多無法忘懷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有很多充滿悲傷的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 黎明一定會來臨的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不必強忍著壓在心頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我確實太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許把莎莉除掉會更好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.55,0:24:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說這個力量會使人孤獨的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.59,0:24:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就必須擁有能忍受這一點的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.56,0:24:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後向毛 討回這筆帳
